OL,3,CKerry Katona reveals rebuilt nose
OL,4,Cafter cocaine addiction
OL,6,FThe 44-year-old Atomic Kitten singer
OL,7,Ffrom Warrington says she started
OL,8,Ftaking drugs at 14, when her mother
OL,9,FSue gave her speed telling her it was
OL,10,Fsherbert.
OL,12,FStardom with the Liverpool girl band
OL,13,FAtomic Kitten in the early 2000s, and
OL,14,Fa string of failed marriages meant she
OL,15,Fwas pursued by paparazzi photographers.
OL,17,FThe mother of five turned to cocaine
OL,18,Fand ended up in what she describes as
OL,19,Fa 'pity party'.
