OL,3,CKerry Katona reveals rebuilt nose
OL,4,Cafter cocaine addiction
OL,6,F"I was acting like the world owed me a
OL,7,Ffavour, like what was happening was
OL,8,Feverybody else's faul", she said. "But
OL,9,FI had to let it go and start taking
OL,10,Fresponsibility for myself".
OL,12,FBut Katona says she has been clean for
OL,13,F14 years and has now had plastic
OL,14,Fsurgery to rebuild her septum, the
OL,15,Fbridge of her nose, which had
OL,16,Fcollapsed after years of drug abuse.
