OL,6,FCartilage from her rib has been used
OL,7,Fto repair that damage, and Ms Katona
OL,8,Fwas happy for Good Morning Britain
OL,9,Fpresenter Richard Madeley to take a
OL,10,Fclose look.
OL,12,FShe says she has been open with her
OL,13,Fchildren about the whole affair.
OL,15,F"It's out there, everywhere", she
OL,16,Fsaid. "With the internet you cannot
OL,17,Fprotect kids from what is going on. I
OL,18,Fwould rather they hear it all from me
OL,19,Fthan someone else".
